query: INSERT INTO files (userId, fileKey, url, filename, mimeType, fileSize, title, description) VALUES (1, 'test/key2.jpg', 'https://example.com/test2.jpg', 'test2.jpg', 'image/jpeg', 452640, 'Wearables Test', 'A detailed post describing how Oura and WHOOP are transforming from wearable devices into full diagnostic ecosystems offering biomarker panels, clinician-reviewed results, AI-driven analysis, and integration of lab data with daily behavior metrics. With Quest Diagnostics powering new biomarker panels and hundreds of thousands on waitlists, these platforms position themselves as continuous-monitoring health operating systems that compete with traditional clinic-based diagnostics. The post argues that the next major shift in healthcare will come from ecosystem builders who merge lifestyle, data, prevention, and diagnostics—blurring the line between consumer tech and clinical care. This file can be used in the Transparent Medical Practice Institute Curriculum to illustrate these dynamics.');
